   "source": [
    "# 🧬 Subliminal Learning: Cloud Master Runner\n",
    "\n",
    "### 🚀 Step 1: Environment Setup\n",
    "Handles Drive mounting and directory setup."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "8d1430b5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "from google.colab import drive\n",
    "\n",
    "# 1. Mount Google Drive\n",
    "drive.mount('/content/drive')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 2. Clone/Update Repo\n",
    "!rm -rf subliminal_learning_Vyshak\n",
    "!git clone https://github.com/vyshakbellur/subliminal_learning_Vyshak.git\n",
    "%cd /content/subliminal_learning_Vyshak/\n",
    "\n",
    "# 3. Install Dependencies\n",
    "%pip install torch biopython numpy pandas matplotlib seaborn gdown"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "rescue_cell_md",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### ⚠️ Data Rescue: Sync Local to Drive\n",
    "**Run this only if you have files in local storage that you want to save to your Drive.**\n",
    "This will copy your current 199 samples to your persistent Drive storage."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "rescue_cell_code",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Ensure the Drive folder exists\n",
    "!mkdir -p /content/drive/MyDrive/MetagenomicData\n",
    "\n",
    "# Copy everything from ephemeral to persistent Drive\n",
    "!cp -v /content/subliminal_learning_Vyshak/data/samples_real/* /content/drive/MyDrive/MetagenomicData/\n",
    "print(\"✅ Local data synced to Google Drive!\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "581a6c5d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 📥 Step 2: Persistent Data Staging (CPU Session)\n",
    "**Run this on a Cheap/CPU Runtime.**\n",
    "Targets 199 samples per environment. It will skip the Marine samples you already have and download the Freshwater ones."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "20f3b336",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Fetch 199 Marine + 199 Freshwater\n",
    "%run run_real_mgnify.py \\\n",
    "    --data-dir \"/content/drive/MyDrive/MetagenomicData\" \\\n",
    "    --n-per-env 199 \\\n",
    "    --skip-training"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "983d5900",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 🛡️ Step 3: Launch Training (GPU Session)\n",
    "Switch to H100 once all downloads are done on the CPU node."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "20f3b337",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%run run_real_mgnify.py \\\n",
    "    --arch ssmoe \\\n",
    "    --data-dir \"/content/drive/MyDrive/MetagenomicData\" \\\n",
    "    --skip-download \\\n",
    "    --epochs 5 \\\n",
    "    --device cuda"
   ]
  }
